  "primaryContentSections": [
    {
      "content": [
        {
          "anchor": "overview",
          "level": 2,
          "text": "Overview",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "Users can track moving objects in video clips to match their movement to a clip, title, logo, generator, or a still image, by using the object-tracker feature in Final Cut Pro. They can also track the shape mask of a video effect, for example a blur, highlight, or color effect, to a moving object in a video clip.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "The object-tracking feature records the movement of an object, for example a reference point, person, or animal, in a video clip and then applies that recorded movement data to another item, which might be a video effect, title, generator, or another video or still-image clip. The result is an animation in which the item ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "inlineContent": [
                {
                  "text": "follows",
                  "type": "text"
                }
              ],
              "type": "emphasis"
            },
            {
              "text": " or moves in conjunction with, the tracked object in the original clip. For example, using the object-tracking technique users can:",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "items": [
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "text": "Add a blurry circle to a personâ€™s face to help preserve anonymity",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "text": "Add a glow effect to the image of jet engines on an airplane streaking through the sky",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "text": "Add the names of swimmers to their moving bodies as they compete in a swim meet",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            }
          ],
          "type": "unorderedList"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "Each object-tracker element consists of one or more tracking shapes. Describe the tracking shapes by using the ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.professionalvideoapplications/documentation/Professional-Video-Applications/tracking-shape",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": " element.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        }
      ],
